title_page: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 5 Evening' game
maintext:
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday evening’s drawing of the Ohio Lottery’s “Pick 5 Evening” game were:
3-1-2-3-5
(three, one, two, three, five)
